{"tid":98381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推薦幾套關於現實災難事故救援的漫畫（已完結）（詳細介紹）","createTime":"2017-01-28T11:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T11:24:33.000Z","uid":79181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c123afc2b35c498c43d4c0b2e41a3a937afe70a3","tid":98381,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"海猿等等係香港多人熟悉嘅救援漫畫我就唔係度介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.特殊救救難隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8o8zes9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8o8zes9.jpg&h=8e78d3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/180016_796bae0683ed91bd45e82e3139d61f67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F180016_796bae0683ed91bd45e82e3139d61f67.jpg&h=c03c0c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1551WML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1551WML.jpg&h=1678342d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左係日本海域進行救援工作，同時係代表日本嘅國際救援部隊。依部漫畫講述男主成長加入部隊過程、日本國際救難隊嘅成立、協助其他經驗不足嘅島國設立相關部隊，當中仲有南亞海潚。<br />\n<br />\n2.海難英雄（海獅）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/181131_c2401ea03f772c37a69f069cb5c7276e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F181131_c2401ea03f772c37a69f069cb5c7276e.jpg&h=7a38b3ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/181149_d60f10c2cf03f43d791b0fadfeee9f17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F181149_d60f10c2cf03f43d791b0fadfeee9f17.jpg&h=b5430a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y63478B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY63478B.jpg&h=f4055086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不同於上面嘅特殊救難隊/海上保安廳，依套係講負責海難現場善後、打撈工作嘅私營民間企業，有些時候甚至會聯合海上保安廳進行救援。順帶一提，我地香港都有類似嘅打撈公司可以係google搵到。另外，依套漫畫就係講現場善後嘅危險、潛水打撈技術、海難影響航運經濟/船運公司嘅立場利益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.Dr.DMAT〜瓦礫下的醫師<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/182232_fa3c15b4e26929b18b3e9108dcec1e28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F182232_fa3c15b4e26929b18b3e9108dcec1e28.jpg&h=e344effc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/182337_c82443b561d4cf256c8bc846c4bc9c2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F182337_c82443b561d4cf256c8bc846c4bc9c2e.jpg&h=c328dbcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohs89Un.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fohs89Un.jpg&h=7338602b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陸地上例如地震、大型火災水災/交通事故、恐襲等等嘅急救單位，但係由醫院當值醫生人手緊急調派到現場進行急救/傷檢分類，唔知道香港有冇依種突發事故嘅機制呢？ 故事講述急救部隊面對嘅壓力、隨機應變力、快速判斷、家屬怪責/醫生自身嘅內疚、仲有各種醫療急救知識、資源短缺/增加器材資金人手所面對嘅政治阻力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.死化妝師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/183418_00c899a688b0adf5ffedf5977937d26a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F183418_00c899a688b0adf5ffedf5977937d26a.jpg&h=b48e7339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8E99fa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8E99fa6.jpg&h=63770ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEr99k9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEr99k9.jpg&h=672eaf3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起急救部隊更加後方處理屍體工作嘅單位，好多時災難事故現場器材/技術/人手不足，導致屍體處理工作馬虎，佢地就係負責接手處理直接面對死亡。依套漫畫可以反映出香港殯儀業技術嘅落後，反思香港社會對殯儀嘅守舊迷信，亦可以讓讀者了解屍體處理嘅工驟/技術、成為死化妝師嘅修讀過程。咁岩我睇依套漫畫嘅時候屋企亦都有人過身，係依本漫畫陪我渡過痛苦嘅時期。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.烈焰赤子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0W2284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0W2284.jpg&h=f906133d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOfGEix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOfGEix.jpg&h=6bf52220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角成為世界知名消防員的故事。畫風、入面設備/技術都比較舊，不過當中嘅熱血同矛盾吸引我一口氣睇完。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完介紹希望大家會對依幾套漫畫有興趣，更加了解依方面單位嘅困難。<br />\n如果你係已經投身從事相關工作/準備畢業加入，亦希望依幾套漫畫可以減輕你嘅壓力/困惑、保持你對工作嘅熱誠/積極。<br />\n如果你係佢地嘅家屬，希望可以令你地更了解更明白佢地嘅工作同犧牲、付出嘅時間，支持佢地多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當中盡力救人、保護自己性命、犧牲少數等等嘅矛盾同內疚，或者英雄主義/團隊合作/服從命令，都好值得我地思考。<br />\n<br />\n近年已經好少有依類型漫畫出現，當中作者親身去趣材嘅照片/訪談亦值得學習，真係好想再有更多可以了解到現今技術、知識，又有劇情嘅漫畫出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0aa2cab381559866aae2a0c3b92b0f2b1c7786","tid":98381,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09e0f5eccec36530aa5785f2f8593bba199a9eed","tid":98381,"uid":71449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0d6e69b0409a539a035e421c14aa5ebf703bb2","tid":98381,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住 放錯去吹水台，想放係動漫台...成日唔記得轉番"},{"pid":"5af28b1027a2a32a74fae4d3fbce9dc695d5fdd4","tid":98381,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海猿等等係香港多人熟悉嘅救援漫畫我就唔係度介紹<img s